x11()

  #plot(x = bb, y = dd[,ii], main = ii, ylab = ii,  xlab = "time", pch = ".", type = "l")

  plot(x = bb, y = preds, main = ii, ylab = ii,  xlab = "time", pch = ".", type = "l")
